import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { FormBuilder, FormGroup, Validators } from '@angular/forms'; @Component({ selector: 'app-ngo-register', templateUrl: './ngo-register.component.html', styleUrls: ['./ngo-register.component.css'] }) export class NgoRegisterComponent { registerForm: FormGroup; constructor(private fb: FormBuilder) { this.registerForm = this.fb.group({ name: ['', Validators.required], email: ['', [Validators.required, Validators.email]], password: ['', [Validators.required, Validators.minLength(6)]], registerNo: ['', Validators.required], address: ['', Validators.required], contactNo: ['', Validators.required], city: ['', Validators.required], website: [''] }); } onSubmit() { if (this.registerForm.valid) { console.log(this.registerForm.value); // Add your registration logic here } else { // Mark all fields as touched to trigger validation messages Object.keys(this.registerForm.controls).forEach(key => { this.registerForm.get(key)?.markAsTouched(); }); } } }
